file.name: response.object.serializer.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: "Test for allOf"
  version: "1"
servers:
  - url: /v1/
paths:
  /date-time:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: date-time handler
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  created_at:
                    type: string
                    format: date-time
                  id:
                    type: number

  /date:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: date handler
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
components:
  schemas:
    Date:
      type: string
      format: date
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id: 
          type: number
        created_at:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/Date"
